    "content": "페이저 변환을 수행할 수 있는 조건\n입력과 출력이 단일 주기와 단일 파장을 가진다. 연산자가 self-adjoint 일 경우, 특수해는 전체해가 된다. 1. Phasor 변환 $$\rA\\cos\\left(\\omega t+\\phi\\right) \\to Ae^{i\\phi}\r$$$$\rA\\sin\\left(\\omega t+\\phi\\right)\\to-iAe^{i\\phi}\r$$$$\rA\\cos\\left(\\omega t+\\phi\\right) \\to Ae^{i\\phi}\r$$$$\rA\\sin\\left(\\omega t+\\phi\\right)\\to-iAe^{i\\phi}\r$$$$\rA\\cos\\left(\\omega t-kx+\\phi\\right)\\to Ae^{i\\left(-kx+\\phi\\right)}\r$$$$\rA\\sin\\left(\\omega t-kx+\\phi\\right)\\to-iAe^{i\\left(-kx+\\phi\\right)}\r$$$$\rAe^{ikx}e^{-i\\omega t}\\to Ae^{ikx}\r$$$e^{-i\\omega t}$를 기준으로,\n$$\r\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}\\to-i\\omega\r$$$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial t^2}\\to-\\omega^2\r$$$e^{+i\\omega t}$를 기준으로,\n$$\r\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}\\to i\\omega\r$$$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial t^2}\\to-\\omega^2\r$$ example1-1)\n$$\ry''-y'-2y=e^{ix}\r$$\rsol\r$$\r\\left(-1-i-2\\right)\\underline{y_p}=1\r$$\r$$\r\\underline{y_p}=-\\frac{1}{3+i}=-\\frac{3-i}{10}\r$$\r$$\ry_{p}=-\\frac{3-i}{10}e^{ix}\r$$\rexample1-2)\n$$\ry''-y'-2y=\\cos x\r$$\rsol\r$$\r\\left(-1-i-2\\right)\\underline{y_p}=1\r$$\r$$\r\\underline{y_p}=-\\frac{1}{3+i}=-\\frac{3-i}{10}\r$$\r$$\ry_{p}=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack-\\frac{3-i}{10}e^{ix}\\right\\rbrack=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack-\\frac{3-i}{10}\\left(\\cos x+i\\sin x\\right)\\right\\rbrack=-\\frac{3}{10}\\cos x-\\frac{1}{10}\\sin x\r$$\rexample2-1)\n$$\ry''-3y'-4y=-ie^{i2x}\r$$\rsol\r$$\r(-4-6i-4)\\underline{y_p}=-1i\r$$\r$$\ry_p=\\frac{i}{8+6i}e^{i2x}\r$$\rexample2-2)\n$$\ry''-3y'-4y=\\sin 2x\r$$\rsol\r$$\r(-4-6i-4)\\underline{y_p}=-1i\r$$\r$$\ry_p=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack\\frac{i}{8+6i}e^{i2x}\\right\\rbrack=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack\\frac{8i-6}{100}\\left(\\cos x+i\\sin x\\right)\\right\\rbrack=-\\frac{3}{50}\\cos x-\\frac{2}{25}\\sin x\r$$\rexample3)\n$$\ry''+y'-2y=4\\sin 2x\r$$\rsol\r$$\r(-4+i-2)\\underline{y_p}=-1i\r$$\r$$\ry_p=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack\\frac{-i}{-4+i-2}e^{i2x}\\right\\rbrack=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack\\frac{6i-1}{37}\\left(\\cos x+i\\sin x\\right)\\right\\rbrack=-\\frac{1}{37}\\cos x-\\frac{6}{37}\\sin x\r$$\rexample4)\n$$\ry''+25y=32\\cos 3x\r$$\rsol\r$$\r(-9+25)\\underline{y_p}=32\r$$\r$$\ry_p=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack\\frac{32}{16}e^{i3x}\\right\\rbrack=2\\cos 3x\r$$\rexample5)\n$$\ry''+4y=\\sin 2x\r$$\rsol\r$$\r\\left(s^2+4\\right)\\underline{y_p}=-1i,\\quad s=2i\r$$\r$$\r\\underline{y_p}=\\frac{1}{s-2i}\\cdot\\frac{-i}{\\left.\\left(s+2i\\right)\\right|_{s=2i}}=x\\cdot\\frac{-i}{4i}=-\\frac14x\r$$\r$$\ry_{p}=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack-\\frac{x}{4}e^{i2x}\\right\\rbrack=-\\frac{x}{4}\\cos2x\r$$\rexample6)\n$$\rx^2y''-2xy'+2y=\\cos x\r$$\rsol\r$$\r\\left(s^2-3s+2\\right)\\underline{y_p}=1\r$$\r$$\r\\underline{y_p}=\\frac{1}{\\left(s^2-3s+2\\right)\\left|_{s=i}\\right.}=\\frac{1}{-3i+1}\r$$\r$$\ry_{p}=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack\\frac{3i+1}{10}\\left(\\cos x+i\\sin x\\right)\\right\\rbrack=\\frac{1}{10}\\cos x-\\frac{3}{10}\\sin x\r$$\rexample7)\n$$\rx^2y''+xy'+25y=3\\sin3x\r$$\rsol\r$$\r\\left(s^2+25\\right)\\underline{y_p}=-3i\r$$\r$$\r\\underline{y_p}=\\frac{-3i}{\\left(s-5i\\right)\\left(s+5i\\right)\\left|_{s=3i}\\right.}\r=-\\frac{3}{16}i\r$$\r$$\ry_{p}=\\operatorname{Re}\\left\\lbrack-\\frac{3}{16}i\\left(\\cos x+i\\sin x\\right)\\right\\rbrack\r=\\frac{3}{16}\\sin x\r$$\rPhasor - Wikipedia\nAnalytic signal - Wikipedia\n9.2 Phasor(페이저) : 네이버 블로그\nsignal - Phasors and Fourier Transform - Electrical Engineering Stack Exchange",
    "description": "페이저 변환을 수행할 수 있는 조건\n입력과 출력이 단일 주기와 단일 파장을 가진다. 연산자가 self-adjoint 일 경우, 특수해는 전체해가 된다. 1. Phasor 변환 $$\rA\\cos\\left(\\omega t+\\phi\\right) \\to Ae^{i\\phi}\r$$$$\rA\\sin\\left(\\omega t+\\phi\\right)\\to-iAe^{i\\phi}\r$$$$\rA\\cos\\left(\\omega t+\\phi\\right) \\to Ae^{i\\phi}\r$$$$\rA\\sin\\left(\\omega t+\\phi\\right)\\to-iAe^{i\\phi}\r$$$$\rA\\cos\\left(\\omega t-kx+\\phi\\right)\\to Ae^{i\\left(-kx+\\phi\\right)}\r$$$$\rA\\sin\\left(\\omega t-kx+\\phi\\right)\\to-iAe^{i\\left(-kx+\\phi\\right)}\r$$$$\rAe^{ikx}e^{-i\\omega t}\\to Ae^{ikx}\r$$$e^{-i\\omega t}$를 기준으로,\n$$\r\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}\\to-i\\omega\r$$$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial t^2}\\to-\\omega^2\r$$$e^{+i\\omega t}$를 기준으로,\n$$\r\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}\\to i\\omega\r$$$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial t^2}\\to-\\omega^2\r$$ example1-1)",
