    "content": "1. Divergence $$\r\\nabla\\cdot\\vec{f}\r=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial\\vec{u}}\\cdot\\vec{f}\r=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_i\\cdot f_j\\hat{u}_j\r=\\frac{\\partial f_j}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_i\\cdot \\hat{u}_j\r=\\frac{\\partial f_j}{\\partial u_j}\r=\\frac{\\partial f_1}{\\partial u_1}+\\frac{\\partial f_2}{\\partial u_2}+\\frac{\\partial f_3}{\\partial u_3}\r$$$$\r\\nabla\\cdot\\vec{f}\r=[\\nabla]_j[\\vec{f}]_j\r=\\frac{\\partial f_j}{\\partial u_j}\r$$ example1) 벡터 $\\vec{u}=u_1\\hat{u}_1+u_2\\hat{u}_2+u_3\\hat{u}_3$ 에 대한 발산을 구하여라.\nsol)\n$$\r\\nabla\\cdot\\vec{u}\r=\\frac{\\partial u_j}{\\partial u_j}\r=3\r$$ 2. 2차 텐서의 divergence $$\r\\nabla\\cdot\\bar{\\bar{A}}\r=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_i\\cdot A_{jk}\\hat{u}_j\\hat{u}_k\r=\\frac{\\partial A_{jk}}{\\partial u_i}(\\hat{u}_i\\cdot\\hat{u}_j)\\hat{u}_k\r=\\frac{\\partial A_{jk}}{\\partial u_i}\\delta_{ij}\\hat{u}_k\r=\\frac{\\partial A_{ik}}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_k\r$$$$\r[\\nabla\\cdot\\bar{\\bar{A}}]_j\r=[\\nabla]_i\\bar{\\bar{A}}_{ij}\r=\\frac{\\partial A_{ij}}{\\partial u_i}\r$$ 3. Laplacian operator $$\r\\nabla^2\r=\\nabla\\cdot\\nabla\r=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_i\\cdot\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial u_j}\\hat{u}_j\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i \\partial u_j}(\\hat{u}_i\\cdot\\hat{u}_j)\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i \\partial u_j}\\delta_{ij}\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i \\partial u_i}\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i^2}\r$$$$\r\\nabla^2\r=[\\nabla]_i[\\nabla]_i\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i^2}\r$$",
    "description": "1. Divergence $$\r\\nabla\\cdot\\vec{f}\r=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial\\vec{u}}\\cdot\\vec{f}\r=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_i\\cdot f_j\\hat{u}_j\r=\\frac{\\partial f_j}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_i\\cdot \\hat{u}_j\r=\\frac{\\partial f_j}{\\partial u_j}\r=\\frac{\\partial f_1}{\\partial u_1}+\\frac{\\partial f_2}{\\partial u_2}+\\frac{\\partial f_3}{\\partial u_3}\r$$$$\r\\nabla\\cdot\\vec{f}\r=[\\nabla]_j[\\vec{f}]_j\r=\\frac{\\partial f_j}{\\partial u_j}\r$$ example1) 벡터 $\\vec{u}=u_1\\hat{u}_1+u_2\\hat{u}_2+u_3\\hat{u}_3$ 에 대한 발산을 구하여라.\nsol)\n$$\r\\nabla\\cdot\\vec{u}\r=\\frac{\\partial u_j}{\\partial u_j}\r=3\r$$ 2. 2차 텐서의 divergence $$\r\\nabla\\cdot\\bar{\\bar{A}}\r=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_i\\cdot A_{jk}\\hat{u}_j\\hat{u}_k\r=\\frac{\\partial A_{jk}}{\\partial u_i}(\\hat{u}_i\\cdot\\hat{u}_j)\\hat{u}_k\r=\\frac{\\partial A_{jk}}{\\partial u_i}\\delta_{ij}\\hat{u}_k\r=\\frac{\\partial A_{ik}}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_k\r$$$$\r[\\nabla\\cdot\\bar{\\bar{A}}]_j\r=[\\nabla]_i\\bar{\\bar{A}}_{ij}\r=\\frac{\\partial A_{ij}}{\\partial u_i}\r$$ 3. Laplacian operator $$\r\\nabla^2\r=\\nabla\\cdot\\nabla\r=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial u_i}\\hat{u}_i\\cdot\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial u_j}\\hat{u}_j\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i \\partial u_j}(\\hat{u}_i\\cdot\\hat{u}_j)\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i \\partial u_j}\\delta_{ij}\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i \\partial u_i}\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i^2}\r$$$$\r\\nabla^2\r=[\\nabla]_i[\\nabla]_i\r=\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial u_i^2}\r$$",
